author: Scott Manley
description:
After a week of almost no information on what happened to NASA's MAVEN we now find out that analysis of the loss of contact suggest the spacecraft may have been spinning and changed to a new orbit:

https://science.nasa.gov/blogs/maven/2025/12/15/nasa-continues-maven-spacecraft-recontact-efforts/

With conjunction coming up in a few days it's possible that the window to save MAVEN may be closing.

Follow me on Twitter for more updates:
https://twitter.com/DJSnM

title: NASA's MAVEN Spacecraft - Spinning Out Of Control?
